Class UserDefinedTree

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Observer, IDecisionInteractive, IDecisionMethod, IDecisionMethodPrority, XMLSerializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
CramerRules, SMARTSTree, SubstructureTree
public class UserDefinedTree
extends AbstractTree
implements IDecisionInteractive

A default decision tree class, implementing IDecisionMethod interface. It stores categories in a IDecisionCategories and the tree itself in a DecisionNodesList. The tree is editable, i.e. rules can be added , removed and modified.

Author:
Nina Jeliazkova Modified 2005-11-10
